snippet.textDisplay: This is pure genius. This song might not be for everyone, it is its novelty and interplay of so many themes, music styles which makes it a treat to listen to. It's a song like no other, which might be its greatest quality. Coke Studio Bharat is doing impeccable work by bringing up alternative and unconventional music styles. These songs do not have an immediate appeal, but are pure works of art. If people say this is overkill, it might as well be said that they haven't explored music enough. A day in the life, Strawberry fields forever are considered paragon of music, but not to everyone's taste, it shouldn't be wrong to compare this song with these classics. This song would only be appreciated much later, it is ahead of its time.
